WorldStage Newsonline– AXA Mansard Insurance Plc, a major player in Nigeria’s insurance sector has released its and subsidiary companies’ unaudited financial statements 31 December 2020 with gross written premium  growth to N47.583 billion from N43.620 billion in 2019 Profit for the year grew by 47.7% to N4.296 billion from N2.908 billion in 2019. WorldStage earlier reported AXA Mansard forecast the fourth quarter (Q4) 2020 with gross premium written of N48.013 billion, a 10% improvement over N43.620 billion in Q4 2019.